title: Highest Vitamin A Supplementation Coverage
description: In 2022, Guinea achieved a Vitamin A supplementation coverage rate of 97% for children aged 6-59 months, one of the highest in the world.

title: Lowest Percentage of Female Secondary School Teachers
description: As of 2021, only 5.8% of secondary school teachers in Guinea were female, one of the lowest percentages globally.

title: Lowest Number of Physicians per 1,000 People
description: In 2022, Guinea had only 0.021 physicians per 1,000 people, one of the lowest ratios in the world.
